    "title": "Senior Financial Analyst - Bandhan Bank - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "Grow your career with Bandhan Bank! We are hiring a Senior Financial Analyst for our Tiruchirappalli team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Bandhan Bank:\nBandhan Bank is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Flexible working hours\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bandhan Bank!",
